:[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:17:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When they came to Capernaum, those who collected the temple tax approached Peter and said, “Doesn’t your teacher pay the temple tax?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 30:13","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 38:26","book":"Exo","chapter":38,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 9:33","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":33,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 30:13","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":13},{"label":"Ex 38:26","book":"Exo","chapter":38,"verse":26},{"label":"Mk 9:33","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":33}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:17:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Yes,” he said."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:17:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“From strangers,” he said. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read Peter said to him"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read Peter said to him"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:17:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“But, so we won’t offend them, go to the sea, cast in a fishhook, and take the first fish that you catch. When you open its mouth you’ll find a coin."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Gk stater, worth 2 double-drachmas"},{"kind":"text","text":" Take it and give it to them for me and you.”"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:29","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 6:61","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":61,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:29","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":29},{"label":"Jn 6:61","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":61}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Gk stater, worth 2 double-drachmas"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099499599}